        public boolean disactivateSubscriber​(java.lang.String idNumber)
        This method disactivates a subscriber, for this, the method uses the id number of the subscriber and look for it in the subscriber list, when the method finds it, changes the state to INACTIVE and the type to NORMAL, also returns true. In the other case, the method doesn't change anything and returns false
        Parameters:
        idNumber - , String, id number of the subscriber that is going to be disactivated
        Returns:
        disactivated, boolean

        public boolean addSubscriber​(java.lang.String idNumber,
                             java.lang.String name,
                             int age,
                             double hoursWillingToWatch,
                             int type)
        This method only works if reapetedId is false. Then, depending on the number that the user has chosen for the type, assign a type value to the clientType variable. Finally, in a cycle, it looks for an available space and in that position it creates a subscriber type object with the data that the user indicated.
        Parameters:
        idNumber - , id number of the subscriber
        name - , name of the subscriber
        age - , age of the subscriber
        hoursWillingToWatch - , hours that the subscriber is willing to watch
        type - , type of subscriber
        Returns:
        added, true if added, else if not

      • addSerie

        public boolean addSerie​(java.lang.String title,
                        java.lang.String synopsis,
                        java.lang.String directorName,
                        int day,
                        int month,
                        int year,
                        java.lang.String protagonistNames,
                        int state,
                        java.lang.String reasonOfCensored,
                        int programmedEpisodesQuantity,
                        int publishedEpisodesQuantity,
                        java.lang.String trailer)
        This method allow us to create a serie. First, it makes sure that the title is not repeated, then it looks for a null position in the product array, wich is the one where the method executes the constructor with all the necesary data
        Parameters:
        title - , title of the serie
        synopsis - , synopsis of the serie, it is an opinion.
        directorName - , name of the director of the serie
        day - , day of the release date
        month - , month of the release date
        year - , year of the release date
        protagonistNames - , the name of the protagonist of the serie separated by commas
        state - , state of the serie. Can be censored or uncesored
        reasonOfCensored - , the reason of why the serie is censored in case it is
        programmedEpisodesQuantity - , the programmed episodes quantity of the first season
        publishedEpisodesQuantity - , the published episodes quantity of the first season
        trailer - , the trailer URL of the first season
        Returns:
        added, boolean.
